transcripts: There's a ton of buzz about some very nasty bugs these days. As pet parents, keeping our four legged family members protected from bites can be a full time job. Protect your pet and your people from insects with apparel and gear from insect shield for pets. A revolutionary defense in the battle against bugs. From the backyard to the backseat, the dangers of insects such as mosquitoes that can carry Zika and heart worm, ticks that can carry lime, the painful attacks of biting flies and ticks are all  a very real issue for our pets. At Insect Shield, we believe that helping to prevent bugs from landing is the best way to keep bugs from biting. Developed for U.S. Military, Insect Shield products offer built in insect protection which is tightly bonded to the fabric, much like the color, so it's not only appropriate for children of any age and puppies, it lasts the expected lifetime of the product. Powerful enough to protect soldiers; gentle enough to put on your puppy. Pick up Insect shield products today.
